    "## Project Overview\n",
    "\n",
    "This project implements two fundamentally different approaches to solving\n",
    "9×9 Sudoku puzzles and exposes them through an interactive **pygame UI**\n",
    "with a cyberpunk-inspired dark/light theme.\n",
    "\n",
    "| Component | Path | Purpose |\n",
    "|-----------|------|---------|\n",
    "| Game engine | `src/sudoku_game.py` | Board generation, validation & state encoding |\n",
    "| Backtracking solver | `src/backtracking_solver.py` | Constraint propagation + MRV backtracking |\n",
    "| RL agent | `src/rl_agent.py` | Double DQN with experience replay |\n",
    "| Configuration | `src/config.py` | All hyperparameters & theme colours |\n",
    "| Training script | `scripts/train.py` | CLI training loop (saves to `models/`) |\n",
    "| Interactive solver | `scripts/solver.py` | Pygame UI for manual play & auto-solve |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Solver Approaches\n",
    "\n",
    "| Approach | Module | Key Idea |\n",
    "|----------|--------|----------|\n",
    "| **Backtracking** | `backtracking_solver.py` | Constraint propagation (naked singles) + recursive search with MRV heuristic |\n",
    "| **Reinforcement Learning** | `rl_agent.py` | Double DQN (CNN + FC) trained via experience replay to select cell/digit actions |\n",
    "\n",
    "### DQN Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "Input: 9×9×10 one-hot state tensor\n",
    "  → Conv2d(10 → 16, 3×3) + ReLU\n",
    "  → Conv2d(16 → 32, 3×3) + ReLU\n",
    "  → Conv2d(32 → 64, 3×3) + ReLU\n",
    "  → Flatten (5,184 features)\n",
    "  → FC(5184 → 256) + ReLU + Dropout(0.1)\n",
    "  → FC(256 → 128)  + ReLU + Dropout(0.1)\n",
    "  → FC(128 → 64)   + ReLU\n",
    "  → FC(64 → 729)   [81 cells × 9 digits]\n",
    "Total parameters ≈ 1.4 M\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key Hyperparameters\n",
    "\n",
    "| Parameter | Value |\n",
    "|-----------|-------|\n",
    "| Learning rate | 0.0005 |\n",
    "| Discount factor (γ) | 0.99 |\n",
    "| ε-greedy: start → end (decay) | 1.0 → 0.05 (×0.995) |\n",
    "| Batch size | 128 |\n",
    "| Replay buffer | 50 000 experiences |\n",
    "| Target network sync | every 100 steps |\n",
    "| Loss function | SmoothL1 (Huber) |\n",
    "| Gradient clipping | max norm 1.0 |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Reward Shaping\n",
    "\n",
    "| Event | Reward |\n",
    "|-------|--------|\n",
    "| Valid move | +1 |\n",
    "| Correct digit (matches solution) | +10 |\n",
    "| Wrong digit | −10 |\n",
    "| Invalid move (constraint violation) | −10 |\n",
    "| Puzzle completion | +200 |\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
